{"tid":379406,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門大水浸既教訓：除左官僚倚靠強國，仲有亂填海","createTime":"2017-08-29T10:08:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T03:14:17.000Z","uid":38255,"like":193,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3afa37f688ca6c855b524758db059ca595704552","tid":379406,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T10:08:01.000Z","msg":"開山起屋有咩潛在問題大家都應該夠清楚，但填海除左生態同景觀之外，我諗香港人都唔係好清楚填海有機會出現咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次澳門內港浸得特別犀利除左係官僚依靠大陸果d，仲有一個原因係亂填海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n埴海個位遮住左原本排水既出海口，同珠海之間既海域填到窄過維港，你填唔填海都係湧咁多海水入黎，你個內港水域越窄，就越多水湧上陸地，澳門又無起返咁上下高既堤壩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ymkg38fd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fymkg38fd&h=821c8f2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過填平左排水渠出海口呢點我唔擔心香港亂黎，啟德跑道同觀塘之間有個窄窄既水體，唔填既原因正正因為果到係啟德河出海口，填左將來落大雨少少上游就真係多得你唔少，就算變做暗渠果部份都會因為排唔走水，路面d水落唔到地底d渠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但將來會唔會盲搶地盲填海就難講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3b8lcrud\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3b8lcrud&h=fb13d9c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而維港經過多次填海，個海平面高左確實係近左陸地唔少但仍然可接受水平，所以自此唔再填得維港係合理安排。當然你可以同海水鬥高，佢升幾多我起幾高堤壩，但到時真係起到十米高都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />至於直接填平咪唔會有水湧入黎，咁就變返上面個問題，維港兩岸d排水渠出海口全部倒出維港，你填平左，佢地排去邊？駁長長管出東西兩邊大海既話一塞左港九兩岸就變到澳門咁落少少雨就浸到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1b04gzfj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1b04gzfj&h=41e71674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢幅係污水渠但雨水都係咁上下咁出海，而且污水渠係咁出海亦代表填平維港後應該港九市區都好似荃灣海之戀咁臭到暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到呢到我諗大家都知連燈仔隨口up既填平維港吐露港會有咩潛在問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將來真係香港變澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n海係填得但唔係亂填，要顧及排水渠等等既野，另外填完後要起一條夠高既堤壩，防止海水倒灌，澳門就係填完就算填海地距離海平面得果1米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，澳門落大雨就內港內陸水浸係因為排水渠出海口畀新既填海地阻住左，海水倒灌就內港沿岸水浸係因為地勢太低又無堤壩，香港要吸取既教訓除左唔可以靠晒支那，仲有就係亂填海既後果。當然香港情況填海造地係最有效既方法，但都要知道填海可能出現既問題，係防洪同填海覓地之間取得平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無整理打得1999左，請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8762177fba658a2b5785ce831581d5781efaf3e","tid":379406,"uid":35205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T10:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a526a37249183e06e7649495e62285035c99fd","tid":379406,"uid":51467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T10:12:02.000Z","msg":"留名 學野"},{"pid":"9727e733dc0a7874ec8454838373ca7bc5ffc8ee","tid":379406,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T10:24:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76b8d947003749f2f33be9bed221e1efd620a495","tid":379406,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T10:30:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>提高臨海高度咪冇問題<br />\n香港當年不惜工本提高哂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇埋排水渠果點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724ae8451ac680137be011182674f22f3a0635e2","tid":379406,"uid":37957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"啟德唔填似係因為保護海港條例多過條明渠"},{"pid":"c2ada2974a772e5801d9b45e2cbc4c50ec5c0af8","tid":379406,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啟德唔填似係因為保護海港條例多過條明渠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係未有條例前，填觀塘繞道對出果部份果陣無填到連埋條跑道廧應該係因為有明渠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6ec7d94c7108ae93ff9cd349747126f9d4c999","tid":379406,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T10:43:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a49d572035d39e0afaa1c073c2218af222648a38","tid":379406,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T10:44:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24d71674fed95b64bcf5a0ff5b9a58fade8a3935","tid":379406,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T10:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6046902abc222951a4e31847dfde95acff634b86","tid":379406,"uid":38255,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>林超英話當年填沙田個陣諗到呢點直情全部填高<br />\n呢個ching又點睇?</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n海係填得但唔係亂填，要顧及排水渠等等既野，<span style=\"color: red;\">另外填完後要起一條夠高既堤壩，防止海水倒灌，澳門就係填完就算填海地距離海平面得果1米</span><br />\n<br />\n我呢段差唔多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除左起夠高堤壩直接填高都可以既，但排水渠出海口點都要保留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外沙田果時由零開始自然可以成個填高佢，但若果係本身已經發展左而家再填出d果種，填完成個海灣海平面上升，你要拉高埋其他沿岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9r87iquj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9r87iquj&h=f465b5ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n例如你填紅色個d位造地，成個吐露港窄左，咁你要拉高埋藍色果堆沿岸既臨海角度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以最好都係向大海填或者係d本身面積較大既水體填（港共個東大嶼都會個位個海域就夠闊），又或者假設發展流浮山，因為后海灣成個香港沿岸都無發展，咁就可以成個填高佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b2c70fd803b9b67537e6daad9b6d96c289c656","tid":379406,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T11:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>林超英話當年填沙田個陣諗到呢點直情全部填高<br />\n呢個ching又點睇?</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n海係填得但唔係亂填，要顧及排水渠等等既野，<span style=\"color: red;\">另外填完後要起一條夠高既堤壩，防止海水倒灌，澳門就係填完就算填海地距離海平面得果1米</span><br />\n<br />\n我呢段差唔多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除左起夠高堤壩直接填高都可以既，但排水渠出海口點都要保留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外沙田果時由零開始自然可以成個填高佢，但若果係本身已經發展左而家再填出d果種，填完成個海灣海平面上升，你要拉高埋其他沿岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9r87iquj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9r87iquj&h=f465b5ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n例如你填紅色個d位造地，成個吐露港窄左，咁你要拉高埋藍色果堆沿岸既臨海<span style=\"color: red;\">高</span>度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以最好都係向大海填或者係d本身面積較大既水體填（港共個東大嶼都會個位個海域就夠闊），又或者假設發展流浮山，因為后海灣成個香港沿岸都無發展，咁就可以成個填高佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f9abcf93205252e1df516c5257978bc1753399f2","tid":379406,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T11:06:59.000Z","msg":"Learn things<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dcd549dce6570c278380b05d4df5c05e0ff5446","tid":379406,"uid":7937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T11:08:14.000Z","msg":"高汁po 留名"},{"pid":"9da6361a64c6d0f9803f6a59ee8d810d6a987112","tid":379406,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"內港個到原本就係咁窄係鬼填先搞到到咁撚窄咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eae74617eb25af284bedf164787d2069191d077","tid":379406,"uid":47729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T11:10:23.000Z","msg":"最好其實係有完善規劃同藍圖下，大量開發棕地。"},{"pid":"f3d5c6e6c4e5380b2778ed6c9114748d99ca9b66","tid":379406,"uid":25973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T11:13:11.000Z","msg":"ching 想問你點睇填