/holland.pk/5uhok1c0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5uhok1c0&h=3be503f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9c7a6052667ef9e53f8456aa1622ae83f24adf6","tid":379406,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主你話唔好填咗啟德條明渠，記得之前有人提出過填咗佢嘅方案:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1021941\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1021941&d=ffQdF0dN00fLNNU72OLo16EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=0cc68dd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1021941&h=ddd968ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1021941</a><br />\n其實除咗明渠之外，暗渠都可以疏導洪水</blockquote>明渠變暗渠唔係問題，啟德河上游都變左暗渠，但填左出海口你就要拉長條渠再遠d出海，渠越長越有機會倒塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人覺得填海最大問題係影響生態同景觀，忽略左香港排洪能力咁高，除左人工設施科技做得好，都得益於長長既海岸線，d水可以有咁快得咁快排出海，唔會成個西九龍既雨水都要靠同一個出海口倒出海，否則實排唔切，將來黃雨都浸到黑雨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251e18400b17c79506efb055aef36cc8c278221e","tid":379406,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T11:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>內港個到原本就係咁窄係鬼填先搞到到咁撚窄咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hu7f9l4v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhu7f9l4v&h=0a7df1d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔係近年填姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />澳葡政府都係無咩規劃藍圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n內港係真係冇咩人工大填過<br />\n佢海岸線越黎越出係幾百年泥沙沖出黎一直推緊向前<br />\n最近期係內港大搞過一次類似填海既都好似係講緊百幾年<br />\n不過個次係將成條海岸線拉直佢起到依家咁<br />\n但個段野真係由頭到尾都唔闊得好多"},{"pid":"e6b6e440e882d6d2773aec663873a6da94cab26d","tid":379406,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"