個去水口對正澳門內港個D又窄又唔係深水既地返<br />\n你開條渠幾闊佢同你湧番幾多上黎都得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nquote錯？我講緊嘅係地下通道排水問題喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢無講錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你明渠定暗渠個去水口係個又窄又淺既港的話，條渠幾闊排水量幾高都無用，出面個港滿到高過條渠個去水口都排唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理論上唔關長唔長事，但你都識講淤塞物，條渠越長越有機會塞，同一條渠要處理越多個地方一樣越易有淤塞物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d483729bb76a1f9411ada2382b94f351748b32","tid":379406,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:07:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明係因為風暴潮導致海水倒灌，連登好似冇乜人講呢樣野？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣咪因為澳門填海無成個好似沙田咁填高晒，沙田當年就係參考溫黛風暴潮去墊高幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但澳門係連落大雨少少內港都會浸得幾犀利，呢樣就關內港窄同排水渠事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b21e45670965853d66e5739f56d980e97cd7e5b","tid":379406,"uid":33605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主你話唔好填咗啟德條明渠，記得之前有人提出過填咗佢嘅方案:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1021941\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1021941&d=ffQdF0dN00fLNNU72OLo16EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=0cc68dd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1021941&h=ddd968ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1021941</a><br />\n其實除咗明渠之外，暗渠都可以疏導洪水</blockquote>明渠變暗渠唔係問題，啟德河上游都變左暗渠，但填左出海口你就要拉長條渠再遠d出海，渠越長越有機會倒塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人覺得填海最大問題係影響生態同景觀，忽略左香港排洪能力咁高，除左人工設施科技做得好，都得益於長長既海岸線，d水可以有咁快得咁快排出海，唔會成個西九龍既雨水都要靠同一個出海口倒出海，否則實排唔切，將來黃雨都浸到黑雨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n排唔排得切係取決於明/暗渠嘅排水量(每秒可處理幾多litre<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)同埋有冇淤塞物，並唔係海岸線同埋排水口嘅多少<br />\n所以其實暗渠都可以處理大量洪水㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梗係唔係啦<br />\n你試下個去水口對正澳門內港個D又窄又唔係深水既地返<br />\n你開條渠幾闊佢同你湧番幾多上黎都得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nquote錯？我講緊嘅係地下通道排水問題喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢無講錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你明渠定暗渠個去水口係個又窄又淺既港的話，條渠幾闊排水量幾高都無用，出面個港滿到高過條渠個去水口都排唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理論上唔關長唔長事，但你都識講淤塞物，條渠越長越有機會塞，同一條渠要處理越多個地方一樣越易有淤塞物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndiu<br />\n我一開頭係講緊雨水跌落嚟要用渠疏導<br />\n你哋就係講緊啲水入又窄又淺嘅內港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗嘅嘢出發點都唔同<br />\n唉...冇嘢啦"},{"pid":"48440d0f70e6f0dbd01e53114fe8bab554784d16","tid":379406,"uid":115279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:12:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ching 想問你點睇填塘？ 填塘會唔會係你心目中比填海好既option？</blockquote><br />\n塘係洪水嚟嘅時候嘅緩衝帶，可以用嚟儲住啲水先，所以填咗又係容易泛濫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffa510b168669744ad8d37bdbd263b7b59c8d1c","tid":379406,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:13:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ching 想問你點睇填塘？ 填塘會唔會係你心目中比填海好既option？</blockquote><br />\n塘係洪水嚟嘅時候嘅緩衝帶，可以用嚟儲住啲水先，所以填咗又係容易泛濫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有大家成日提既食水問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe020b604fc1a4f6bd7a4b6feb29bb001fae7c23","tid":379406,"uid":46737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"好似半島外港仲打算再填個島<br />\nBtw， 橫琴島應該都影響左內港去水"},{"pid":"7c8c76eaa450eb102dfda95de0768b5c53f855d7","tid":379406,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T18:49:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F1j3tApnzJw?t=12m52s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF1j3tApnzJw%3Ft%3D12m52s&d=ffQdF0dN00fLNNU72OLo16EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=41d061ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F1j3tApnzJw?t=12m52s</a><br />\n<br />\n呢段有講內港填到窄晒導致重災<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b16af0c1ea7e7168804d6692f9b67dfbc6cd38","tid":379406,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T18:54:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/F1j3tApnzJw?t=12m52s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF1j3tApnzJw%3Ft%3D12m52s&d=ffQdF0dN00fLNNU72OLo16EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=41d061ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F1j3tApnzJw?t=12m52s</a><br />\n<br />\n呢段有講內港填到窄晒導致重災<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/76vksdth\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F76vksdth&h=2247b6bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2288311576a8fe17e75f8ceab84acb84cab0d98c","tid":379406,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T20:29:26.000Z","msg":"以前港英規劃係將九龍灣填晒出去，維港變咗條河咁，係後來有人挑戰，司法覆核先冇咗件事喎。技術上應該係計過排水冇問題先做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9366e80f4eaa717b959c3a9a86eda3cc0c4ec36e","tid":379406,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T20:32:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似半島外港仲打算再填個島<br />\nBtw， 橫琴島應該都影響左內港去水</blockquote><br />\n直頭係啦<br />\n珠海嗰邊根本填到貼撚晒澳門<br />\ncctvb個維穩報導淡化晒珠海嗰邊填海填成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a12f350bcac373f639828c0b04051b0f692671","tid":379406,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T20:44:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似半島外港仲打算再填個島<br />\nBtw， 橫琴島應該都影響左內港去水</blockquote><br />\n直頭係啦<br />\n珠海嗰邊根本填到貼撚晒澳門<br />\ncctvb個維穩報導淡化晒珠海嗰邊填海填成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/9-02-2017/zcqiBN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F9-02-2017%2FzcqiBN.gif&h=6688e5e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n86年果陣都仲可以，去到2000年就無救啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63eb34e8af20daec8fe0fde0ff9eb4751feee0b6","tid":379406,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T21:17:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>林超英話當年填沙田個陣諗到呢點直情全部填高<br />\n呢個ching又點睇?</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n海係填得但唔係亂填，要顧及排水渠等等既野，<span style=\"color: red;\">另外填完後要起一條夠高既堤壩，防止海水倒灌，澳門就係填完就算填海地距離海平面得果1米</span><br />\n<br />\n我呢段差唔多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除左起夠高堤壩直接填高都可以既，但排水渠出海口點都要保留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外沙田果時由零開始自然可以成個填高佢，但若果係本身已經發展左而家再填出d果種，填完成個海灣<span style=\"color: blue;\">海平面上升</span>，你要拉高埋其他沿岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9r87iquj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9r87iquj&h=f465b5ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n例如你填紅色個d位造地，成個吐露港窄左，咁你要拉高埋藍色果堆沿岸既臨海角度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以最好都係向大海填或者係d本身面積較大既水體填（港共個東大嶼都會個位個海域就夠闊），又或者假設發展流浮山，因為后海灣成個香港沿岸都無發展，咁就可以成個填高佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔明點解填海會令海平面上升<br />\n啲水唔係可以流走咩？"},{"pid":"55c90c3bebe34026543082f3495a0789bd51d8b9","tid":379406,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T21:29:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似半島外港仲打算再填個島<br />\nBtw， 橫琴島應該都影響左內港去水</blockquote><br />\n直頭係啦<br />\n珠海嗰邊根本填到貼撚晒澳門<br />\ncctvb個維穩報導淡化晒珠海嗰邊填海填成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/9-02-2017/zcqiBN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F9-02-2017%2FzcqiBN.gif&h=6688e5e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n86年果陣都仲可以，去到2000年就無救啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n關閘嗰邊原本一條沙堤<br />\n珠海嗰邊即頭一片汪洋<br />\n而家兩邊都住滿晒人<br />\n<br />\n原本啲海島之間形成嘅自然景觀幾靚<br />\n應該就係呢啲地方養蠔<br />\n我仲記得路氹未填海時<br />\n坐車經過條連貫公路，落霞映照兩邊平靜嘅水面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}